childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0The Market...^$1Hyrule Field...^$2The Lost Woods...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Zora's River...^$3Death Mountain Trail...^$4Goron City...^$5Kakariko Village...^$6Gerudo Valley...^$7Haunted Wasteland...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to collect&6 Spiritual Stones and Medallions.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be hidden somewhere %rinside&its castle%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: What about Zelda makes you think&she'd be a better ruler than I?^I saved Lon Lon Ranch,&fed the hungry,&and my castle floats.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rthe house of the dead%w!
sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%rthe house of the dead%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rthe Graveyard%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--DampÃ©
gregText: By the way, if you're interested,&I saw the shiniest %gGreen Rupee%w&somewhere in%g Kakariko&Village%w.^It's said to have %rmysterious&powers%w...^But then, it could just be another&regular rupee.&Oh well.
sariaText: Did you feel the %gsurge of&magic%w recently? A mysterious&bird told me it came from %gGoron&City%w.^You should check that place out,&@!$C
